# Google OAuth Client ID (créer dans Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials)
# Type: OAuth 2.0 Client ID, Application type: Web application
# Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173 (dev) + https://your-domain.com (prod)
# Authorized redirect URIs: non requis (implicit flow côté client)
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
